<template>

      class="el-menu-demo"

      @select="handleSelect"

    <el-sub-menu index="2">
      <template #title>Workspace</template>

      </el-sub-menu>
    </el-sub-menu>
    <el-menu-item index="3" disabled>Info</el-menu-item>

  </el-menu>
  <div class="h-6" />

    </el-sub-menu>
    <el-menu-item index="3" disabled>Info</el-menu-item>
